The real question is, who misses the other more when we travel? 🥹

I’ve always looked forward to my travels, whether it’s a long trip to explore a new country, or a quick one for work. But leaving my baby is always the hardest part. The way he just knows, the minute I start packing. The way he finds his way into my suitcase, as if I can just zip it up and take him with me. The way he sulks as I leave the house… walking away, is always the hardest thing to do ❤️‍🩹
So most times, coming home is more exciting than leaving for that vacation. 
Because this is what I come home to. 
Unconditional love. A feeling of knowing that no matter how many times I leave, he will be waiting for me to come back to him 🧳🤎 @buddycocker111 

[ Pet , Dogs Of Instagram , Unconditional Love , Home ]

#UnconditionalLove #ComingHome #MyBaby

Dot, swipe, GLOW ✨

@romerojennings , Director of Makeup @maccosmeticsindia dropped by Tira Studios to show us (and you) how to create @maccosmeticsindia ‘s Studio Radiance glowy look, right in time for the best season of the year!

1. It all starts with the M•A•C Studio Radiance Serum-Powered foundation for a flawless base
2. Get a luminous lift with the Studio Radiance 24-HR Luminous Lift Concealer, which conceals, corrects and lifts for a skin-like finish
3. Pro tip: use the Glow Play Cushiony Blush in the shade Totally Synced on the cheek and a little bit above the brow for to elevate the face 
4. Finish off with the Glow Play Talk Lip Balm in the shade Trick for a pop of colour

Follow @tirabeauty for more expert tips and advice.
